relation: Darrow4 - #03 The captain is tough, but not really open minded. You'd be jaded, too, if you fought 4000 battles in Dinosaur Forest and realized General Leo wasn't coming back.
Darrow4 - #04 After checking a nearby house, Ness discovers the key to getting into the Stoic Club. Surely a club this secretive must be pretty amazing, huh?
Darrow4 - #05 Before the group can advance further, a sudden call comes in for Jeff. It's Tony! ....It's Tony.
Darrow4 - #06 Tony, after outright breaking the fourth wall, prompts the player for their name. Are you a bad enough dude to stop Giygas?
Darrow4 - #07 Heading into the Stoic Club proves to be a bigger task than expected. I wonder if these guys submit to fan theories?
